{{Jainism}}
'''Vidyananda''' was an 8th-century Indian [[Jain monk]].

==Life==
Vidyananda was a [[Jainism|Jain]] scholar and monk.{{sfn|Nakamura|1983|p=73}} He was born in 750 AD and died in 800.{{sfn|Nakamura|1983|p=88}}

==Works==
He wrote ''Ashtasahasri'' which is a commentary on [[Samantabhadra (Jain monk)|Samantabhadra's]] ''Devagamastotra''.{{sfn|Nakamura|1983|p=73}}

